CHANGELOG.md
     1‚Üí# Changelog
     2‚Üí
     3‚ÜíAll notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.
     8‚Üí## [1.2.1] - 2025-10-26
     9‚Üí
    10‚Üí- Move more config to `pyproject.toml`, removed `setup.cfg`
    11‚Üí- Add support for reading `.env` from FIFOs (Unix) by [@sidharth-sudhir] in [#586]
    13‚Üí## [1.2.0] - 2025-10-26
    14‚Üí
    15‚Üí- Upgrade build system to use PEP 517 & PEP 518 to use `build` and `pyproject.toml` by [@EpicWink] in [#583]
    16‚Üí- Add support for Python 3.14 by [@23f3001135] in [#579](https://github.com/theskumar/python-dotenv/pull/563)
    17‚Üí- Add support for disabling of `load_dotenv()` using `PYTHON_DOTENV_DISABLED` env var. by [@matthewfranglen] in [#569]
    19‚Üí## [1.1.1] - 2025-06-24
    20‚Üí
    21‚Üí### Fixed
    22‚Üí
    23‚Üí* CLI: Ensure `find_dotenv` work reliably on python 3.13 by [@theskumar] in [#563](https://github.com/theskumar/python-dotenv/pull/563)
    24‚Üí* CLI: revert the use of execvpe on Windows by [@wrongontheinternet] in [#566](https://github.com/theskumar/python-dotenv/pull/566)
