   258‚Üí## 0.10.3
   259‚Üí
   260‚Üí- Improve interactive mode detection ([@andrewsmith])([#183]).
   261‚Üí- Refactor parser to fix parsing inconsistencies ([@bbc2])([#170]).
   262‚Üí  - Interpret escapes as control characters only in double-quoted strings.
   263‚Üí  - Interpret `#` as start of comment only if preceded by whitespace.
   265‚Üí## 0.10.2
   266‚Üí
   267‚Üí- Add type hints and expose them to users ([@qnighy])([#172])
   268‚Üí- `load_dotenv` and `dotenv_values` now accept an `encoding` parameter, defaults to `None`
   269‚Üí  ([@theskumar])([@earlbread])([#161])
   270‚Üí- Fix `str`/`unicode` inconsistency in Python 2: values are always `str` now. ([@bbc2])([#121])
   271‚Üí- Fix Unicode error in Python 2, introduced in 0.10.0. ([@bbc2])([#176])
   273‚Üí## 0.10.1
   274‚Üí- Fix parsing of variable without a value ([@asyncee])([@bbc2])([#158])
   276‚Üí## 0.10.0
   277‚Üí
   278‚Üí- Add support for UTF-8 in unquoted values ([@bbc2])([#148])
   279‚Üí- Add support for trailing comments ([@bbc2])([#148])
   280‚Üí- Add backslashes support in values ([@bbc2])([#148])
   281‚Üí- Add support for newlines in values ([@bbc2])([#148])
   282‚Üí- Force environment variables to str with Python2 on Windows ([@greyli])
   283‚Üí- Drop Python 3.3 support ([@greyli])
   284‚Üí- Fix stderr/-out/-in redirection ([@venthur])
   287‚Üí## 0.9.0
   288‚Üí
   289‚Üí- Add `--version` parameter to cli ([@venthur])
   290‚Üí- Enable loading from current directory ([@cjauvin])
   291‚Üí- Add 'dotenv run' command for calling arbitrary shell script with .env ([@venthur])
   293‚Üí## 0.8.1
   294‚Üí
   295‚Üí-   Add tests for docs ([@Flimm])
   296‚Üí-   Make 'cli' support optional. Use `pip install python-dotenv[cli]`. ([@theskumar])
   298‚Üí## 0.8.0
   299‚Üí
   300‚Üí-   `set_key` and `unset_key` only modified the affected file instead of
   301‚Üí    parsing and re-writing file, this causes comments and other file
   302‚Üí    entact as it is.
   303‚Üí-   Add support for `export` prefix in the line.
   304‚Üí-   Internal refractoring ([@theskumar])
   305‚Üí-   Allow `load_dotenv` and `dotenv_values` to work with `StringIO())` ([@alanjds])([@theskumar])([#78])
   307‚Üí## 0.7.1
   308‚Üí
   309‚Üí-   Remove hard dependency on iPython ([@theskumar])
   311‚Üí## 0.7.0
   312‚Üí
   313‚Üí-   Add support to override system environment variable via .env.
   314‚Üí    ([@milonimrod](https://github.com/milonimrod))
   315‚Üí    ([\#63](https://github.com/theskumar/python-dotenv/issues/63))
   316‚Üí-   Disable ".env not found" warning by default
   317‚Üí    ([@maxkoryukov](https://github.com/maxkoryukov))
   318‚Üí    ([\#57](https://github.com/theskumar/python-dotenv/issues/57))
   320‚Üí## 0.6.5
   321‚Üí
   322‚Üí-   Add support for special characters `\`.
   323‚Üí    ([@pjona](https://github.com/pjona))
   324‚Üí    ([\#60](https://github.com/theskumar/python-dotenv/issues/60))
   326‚Üí## 0.6.4
   327‚Üí
   328‚Üí-   Fix issue with single quotes ([@Flimm])
   329‚Üí    ([\#52](https://github.com/theskumar/python-dotenv/issues/52))
   331‚Üí## 0.6.3
   332‚Üí
   333‚Üí-   Handle unicode exception in setup.py
   334‚Üí    ([\#46](https://github.com/theskumar/python-dotenv/issues/46))
   336‚Üí## 0.6.2
   337‚Üí
   338‚Üí-   Fix dotenv list command ([@ticosax](https://github.com/ticosax))
   339‚Üí-   Add iPython Support
   340‚Üí    ([@tillahoffmann](https://github.com/tillahoffmann))
   342‚Üí## 0.6.0
   343‚Üí
   344‚Üí-   Drop support for Python 2.6
   345‚Üí-   Handle escaped characters and newlines in quoted values. (Thanks
   346‚Üí    [@iameugenejo](https://github.com/iameugenejo))
   347‚Üí-   Remove any spaces around unquoted key/value. (Thanks
   348‚Üí    [@paulochf](https://github.com/paulochf))
   349‚Üí-   Added POSIX variable expansion. (Thanks
   350‚Üí    [@hugochinchilla](https://github.com/hugochinchilla))
   352‚Üí## 0.5.1
   353‚Üí
   354‚Üí-   Fix `find_dotenv` - it now start search from the file where this
   355‚Üí    function is called from.
   357‚Üí## 0.5.0
   358‚Üí
   359‚Üí-   Add `find_dotenv` method that will try to find a `.env` file.
   360‚Üí    (Thanks [@isms](https://github.com/isms))
   362‚Üí## 0.4.0
   363‚Üí
   364‚Üí-   cli: Added `-q/--quote` option to control the behaviour of quotes
   365‚Üí    around values in `.env`. (Thanks
   366‚Üí    [@hugochinchilla](https://github.com/hugochinchilla)).
   367‚Üí-   Improved test coverage.
